Text: The ring is a type of birth control. It’s a small, flexible ring that you put inside your vagina for three weeks and it prevents ovulation (when your body releases an egg) - no egg, no baby! You take it out the week of your period and then pop a new one in. Super easy and you won’t even feel it.
